precis:
Amendment to the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS Schedule No. 864
establishing maximum residue limits (MRLs) on the amount of the herbicide
"CLETHODIM" that can be detected on soybeans, potatoes and flax seed,
being a new, selective, cyclohexanedione herbicide used for the control of
a wide range of annual and perennial grasses.
